                    ********************************
                    ***   GLOSSARY USER MANUAL   ***
                    ********************************

 ** If you want to know russian meaning of english word activate GLOSSARY
 ** with ALT-G hot key then type word in ENGLISH EDITOR WINDOW in lower case
 ** english letters (you can use also blank, hyphen and dot symbols) and press
 ** ENTER key.
 ** If GLOSSARY found searching word in base files RUSSIAN EDITOR WINDOW
 ** will be opened with translated russian string inside it. If search fails
 ** generates beep and empty string put down in RUSSIAN EDITOR WINDOW.
 ** Now you can edit russian string (valid characters are russian lower case
 ** letters, blank, hyphen, dot) and update or create record in GLOSSARY base
 ** file pressing ENTER key.
 ** From ENGLISH(RUSSIAN) EDITOR WINDOW you can get into MENU WINDOW through
 ** F1 key. Navigate menu bar with arrow keys and choose option with ENTER
 ** key.
 ** GLOSSARY can read english words from current text page in two modes :
 ** 1) From cursor position in any text editor. You can set this mode
 ** in MENU WINDOW choosing CURSOR option.
 ** 2) Scanning current text page and mark only english words by changing
 ** video attributes. You can set this mode in MENU WINDOW choosing SCANER
 ** option.
 ** Choose EDITOR option in MENU WINDOW if you want return to ENGLISH EDITOR
 ** WINDOW to input new word.
 ** Editor string can be squeezed if you choose COMPRESS option in MENU
 ** WINDOW.
 ** Use ESC key or QUIT! option to exit GLOSSARY. 













